article.headline: Bostick leads Cal State Northridge over Cal State Bakersfield 76-71
article.description: — Dionte Bostick's 27 points helped Cal State Northridge defeat Cal State Bakersfield 76-71 on Thursday night.
article.linkText: Bostick leads Cal State Northridge over Cal State Bakersfield 76-71
article.story: BAKERSFIELD, Calif. -- — Dionte Bostick's 27 points helped Cal State Northridge defeat Cal State Bakersfield 76-71 on Thursday night. Bostick also contributed four steals for the Matadors (17-9, 8-6 Big West Conference). De'Sean Allen-Eikens scored 21 points on 8-for-11 shooting. Corey Stephenson led the way for the Roadrunners (10-15, 5-9) with 17 points and eight rebounds. Cameron Wilbon also had 17 points, while Dalph Panopio scored 15. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
